DESCRIPTION:Jamie\, open the app\, see today's workout\, and let the first step be enough.\\n\\nUse the app link here: https://jamie-x-sfitness-app-six.vercel.app/\\n\\nIf the trainer on video moves faster or heavier\, you do not need to match that. Clean and controlled wins.
